">$5/mo</strong>.\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"hero__ctas\">\n        <a href=\"#demo-placeholder\" class=\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\">Build Your Association Portal &rarr;</a>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\" class=\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\" target=\"_blank\">Fork on GitHub</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"hero__aside\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ======== FEATURES ======== -->\n  <section class=\"section section--white\" id=\"features\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"section-header\">\n        <p class=\"t-overline\">Built for Associations</p>\n        <h2 class=\"t-display t-display--lg\">Everything your professional association needs.</h2>\n        <p class=\"t-body--lg mt-2\">Six association-specific features, ready out of the box. Toggle them on with a config flag.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-card__icon\">&#128101;</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__name\">Member Directory</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__desc\">Searchable profiles with company names, titles, specialties, and contact info. Filter by region or expertise.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-card__icon\">&#127963;&#65039;</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__name\">Committee Management</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__desc\">Working groups with chairs, members, meeting schedules, and shared documents. Track committee activities.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-card__icon\">&#127915;</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__name\">Conference &amp; Events</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__desc\">Conference registration, session tracks, speaker bios, and attendee networking. Multi-day event support.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-card__icon\">&#128218;</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__name\">Resource Library</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__desc\">Whitepapers, webinar recordings, industry reports, and best practices. Tier-gated access control.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-card__icon\">&#127941;</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__name\">Membership Tiers</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__desc\">Fellow, Member, Associate, and Student tiers with different permissions, pricing, and resource access.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-card__icon\">&#128202;</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__name\">Member Insights</div>\n          <div class=\"feature-card__desc\">AI-powered engagement analytics. Spot at-risk renewals, identify active contributors, and track growth.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ======== PRICING ======== -->\n  <section class=\"section section--cream section--dotted\" id=\"pricing\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"section-header section-header--center\">\n        <p class=\"t-overline\">Pricing</p>\n        <h2 class=\"t-display t-display--lg\">Flat pricing. No per-member fees. Ever.</h2>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"plans-grid\">\n        <div class=\"plan-card\">\n          <div class=\"plan-card__name\">DIY Template</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__price\">Free</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__price-sub\">+ $5&ndash;20/mo Run402 hosting</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__desc\">\"For developers and AI agents.\"</div>\n          <ul class=\"plan-card__features\">\n            <li>Full source code (open source)</li>\n            <li>All features included</li>\n            <li>Self-deploy to Run402</li>\n            <li>Community support</li>\n          </ul>\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/kychee-com/wildlychee\" class=\"btn btn--outline\" target=\"_blank\">Fork on GitHub</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"plan-card plan-card--featured\">\n          <div class=\"plan-card__name\">Studio Build</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__price\">$29</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__price-sub\">one-time + $5&ndash;20/mo hosting</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__desc\">\"Tell us about your association. Live in 5 minutes.\"</div>\n          <ul class=\"plan-card__features\">\n            <li>AI investigates your existing site</li>\n            <li>Guided interview &rarr; custom portal</li>\n            <li>Brand colors, logo, content migrated</li>\n            <li>Multi-language translation</li>\n            <li>Chrome-verified deployment</li>\n          </ul>\n          <a href=\"#demo-placeholder\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">Build My Portal &rarr;</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"plan-card\">\n          <div class=\"plan-card__name\">Lychee Pro</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__price\">$9&ndash;29/mo</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__price-sub\">ongoing, cancel anytime</div>\n          <div class=\"plan-card__desc\">\"Your portal evolves with you.\"</div>\n          <ul class=\"plan-card__features\">\n            <li>Ongoing AI customization agent</li>\n            <li>Feature requests via chat</li>\n            <li>Priority support</li>\n            <li>Advanced analytics</li>\n          </ul>\n          <a href=\"#demo-placeholder\" class=\"btn btn--outline\">Learn More</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ======== FINAL CTA ======== -->\n  <section class=\"section section--indigo final-cta\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <h2 class=\"t-display t-display--lg\">Stop paying per-member. Start owning your portal.</h2>\n      <p class=\"t-body--lg\">Open source. Flat pricing. AI-powered. Yours forever.</p>\n      <div class=\"final-cta__buttons\">\n       